title: Poppy Flower, 12 Peach Crepe Paper Poppies, Paper Flower Bouquet, Handmade Flowers, Poppy Flower Gift, Wedding Bouquet, Eco Friendly Gift
description:
Important Holiday Deadlines
As of today (11/22/2020) my projected cut off for delivery by Christmas is 12/11/2020.  USPS is expecting delays due to the unprecedented amount of packages to pass thru their facilities.  Please place your orders as soon as possible.  
Turnaround time may be different for each product.  Turnaround time or processing time is different than shipping transit time.  I can guarantee that your items will ship within the specific item processing time but cannot guarantee transit time.  

One Dozen Handmade Peach Crepe Paper Poppies.

Poppies vary in size from 2 1/2" to 3 1/2" each on 10” recycled silver aluminum wire stem. Each bloom has an attached felt leaf. Centers are black felt.

Each flower is hand crafted from start to finish. Each poppy is unique to themselves and no 2 exactly alike.

No wilting, no watering and always in season.

Ready for your own build a bouquet or display in vases for centerpieces.

All our flowers are handmade from recycled and sustainable materials.

Why Mabel Lane flower stems are silver and not the typical green: Aluminum is a 100% recyclable and sustainable metal. Almost 80% of aluminum produced is still in use and saves more than 90% of the energy to make new aluminum. The moment I add harmful non-biodegradable floral tape or use chemical filled painted floral stems to get the green color I take a step away from my pursuit of eco-thoughtful flowers. All my stems can be clipped and safely recycled without any effort from my customers.

title: Downloadable Fine Crepe Paper Rose Template/PDF Printable Download/DIY Paper Flower Template/Paper Rose Template/Paper Flower Tutorial
description:
Make your own crepe paper roses using this downloadable digital template.

*This template is meant for THIN or FINE WEIGHT crepe paper*
By fine crepe paper, this means you should be able to see the shadow of your hand through the crepe paper. A 60 gram or 90 gram weight of paper is recommended.

The download includes:
- Printable PDF template for regular 8.5" by 11" printer paper
- Written step-by-step instructions

Photos showing each step can also be found on my website www.citrinepaperflowers.com (and while you are there, sign up for my e-newsletter to get special freebies!)

You will need to provide your own supplies. Supplies you will need for making 1 rose:
- Scissors
- Glue
- Printer paper for printing out the template
- Fine weight crepe paper (about a 15" by 20" area of paper for the petals, and an 8" by 10" area of green paper)
- Cotton ball or crumpled ball of paper for the flower center
- Floral wire (20 gauge or thicker) or a barbecue skewer for the stem
- Thin floral wire (about 26 gauge for wiring the leaf)

Benefits:
- Save money by making your own wedding bouquet or flower arrangement!
- You can re-use the template to make as many flowers as you want
- Handmade flowers are unique and they don't wilt so you can cherish them forever

- This template is meant to be used with crepe paper, and not cardstock or other types of paper that don't stretch.

title: Paper Peonies Kit
description:
PAPER PEONY KIT

Create your very own Paper Blooms with our fantastic Paper Peony Flower Kit.

What's In The Box
Each kit contains Italian Crepe Paper, Florist tape, Florist wires, Printed Template, Printed how to booklet and a digital download of a full colour PDF.  

What's Not In The Box
You will need scissors and adhesive, some kits may require a coloured pen or pencil.

Paper Bloom DIY Kits are available in a variety of designs. This kit will make 1 giant peony.

Not sure what colour you prefer? Message me and I can show you some examples of your favourite colours, Your chosen colour will then be lovingly packed and wrapped in tissue, placed in a sturdy box and wrapped in brown paper before being mailed to you. This kit can be gift wrapped and sent direct to the recipient as a gift.

Easy to follow instructions with crystal clear photographs of every step will allow you to quickly learn how to cut and shape all the petals needed to make a Beautiful Bloom, perfect for display in a vase or bouquet. 

Support is available via email or social media if you need a few pointers

Delivery is included in the price of this craft kit.

Suitable for beginners and children over 12 Years. Under 12's may be able to complete with close supervision if you are using hot glue.

Please note the crepe paper used in these kits of florist quality and thicker than normal craft crepe. Colours seen on screen may very slightly from those received dependent on your monitor settings.
For best results display out of direct sunlight to prevent fading, Once completed flowers can be dusted occasionally by shaking gently or blowing with a hair dryer on a cool setting

title: Cosmos Paper Flower Kit  for 1/12th scale Dollhouses, Florists and Miniature Gardens
description:
A  1/12th or 1” scale paper flower  kit to make 10 Cosmos flowers in either Pink or White. The foliage is NOT included.

I used Reindeer moss for the foliage, unfortunately I no longer sell this product, but it should be easily available from model railway suppliers and some florists or hobby shops.
Easy to make these add an airy touch to a summer garden.

The kit includes punched coloured paper petals, wires and illustrated instructions.

To Finish this Kit
 You will need:

Fine pointed tweezers
Tacky glue
Eraser (for moulding petals and leaves)
A pot or vase or perhaps you are planting this in a flower bed?




I hope your dolls house garden grows and flourishes, no weeding, no pests just delightful flowers!

The kits are all my own original copyrighted designs. They are not to be copied and reproduced for any reason.

title: Baby Name Sign with Paper Flower Wall Decor Above Crib, Nursery Decor, Dusty Rose Large Paper Flowers, Personalized Nursery Wall Art Set
description:
Baby name sign with paper flowers wall decor above crib is a beautiful idea for nursery decoration. Nice dusty rose half-open peony with buds, charming roses and fine lilies with hydrangeas will turn the room of your little princess into blooming garden. Together with baby name they create personalized nursery wall art set
.
Any wedding or party will be more stunning and magnificent with such a set of large paper flowers or even the whole theme! They are wonderful for nursery, girls room or any elegant feminine space. Have a fun using them as thank-you gift or house warming. These paper flowers will make any space look like a display.
.
Extremely rare find for one who looks something extraordinarily tender and sophisticated for a wedding ceremony, bridal or baby shower backdrop. 
.

*********************** WHAT YOU GET ***********

There are 3 options for your choice:

1. flowers only;
2. name only
3. flowers with name or initials


*************************** SIZE ***********************

The dimension of whole arrangement is 2,7'x2,7'/ 0.8x0.8 m

The set of 10 flowers includs:
   1 half open peony: 8"/ 20 cm
   1 double bud of peony: 3"+1"/ 7+3 cm
   1 rose: 12"/30 cm
   2 roses: 8"/20 cm
   1 roses: 6"/15 cm
   2 lilies: 9"/22 cm
   2 hydrangeas: 6"/15 cm

Name sign is available in 5 sizes (length):
   - 14"/ 35 cm: not recommended for names with more than 5 letters;
   - 18"/ 45 cm: not recommended for names with more than 7 letters;
   - 22"/ 55 cm;
   - 26"/ 66 cm;
   - 30"/ 76 cm

(!) Customizing is welcomed 

***************************COLORS ************************

For flowers you can choose variety of colors from our color chart (you can see one in the photo gallery of this listing). Indicate their names in the personalization field. Select as many colors as you wish, but we would not recommend more than 2 colors for this set.

For this set were used:
  - dusty rose
  

For name sign we suggest 3 options (look into the photo gallery):
   - silver mirror acrylic;
   - gold mirror acrylic;
   - white acrylic

This set was made with 18"/45 cm name and font #1 of white acrylic

(!) Please note, colours can vary slightly due to monitor settings

********************** HOW TO FIX ****************

Peonies have metallic loops on the basis. Designed for hanging by hook, which is fixed to a wall with Command 3M damage free tape (included into the package).
.
Roses and other flowers have piece of damage free double sided tape on their backs. You only need to remove protection film and attach the flowers to a wall
.
A name comes with damage free double sided tape on the back

******************** HOW TO ARRANGE FLOWERS ******************

All flowers come separately and you need to arrange them on the wall according to your wish. The photo shows only an example of how this can be done, although it is not necessary to adhere to this form. However, if you like the composition in the photo and you want to achieve the same result, we can add a template with layout of the flowers. If you need it, just add a note upon ordering

*********************** OUR CLIENTS COMMENTS ******************

" I'll be honest, in my extensive search for decor, I tried to find a cheaper alternative on Etsy (having a baby is already so expensive!), but nothing compared to your quality. You're very detail-oriented and your work shows how much you care. I'm so glad that I didn't cut the cost for something that wasn't as perfect. Thank you for doing what you do!"

********************* OTHER SIMILAR WORKS ************

.

.

.
All flowers: https://www.etsy.com/shop/PapierDeco

***************************************************************

Your items will be shipped after the payment is cleared. 100% payment is required on all custom orders.
.
Please make sure that you specified a valid address.
.
We use only air mail with a tracking code. Delivery is guaranteed.
.
Normally we ship the product within 5 business days but please allow us a bit more if your order significantly exceeds one piece.
.

.
Flowers are carefully packed and fixed. All the boxes are provided with partitions to separate flowers from each other and to ensure delivery in excellent condition.
.
